name: hana makihatayama 巻機山 花(ハナちゃん) - magical doremi (ojamajo doremi)
description:
LORA by hana makihatayama in magical doremi, learning through official and fan art.

Trigger: 'makihatayama_hana'.

It is also possible to change clothes by using the 'hanacos01' trigger for everyday clothes and the 'hanawitch' trigger for witch clothes.

Casual Trigger: 'hanacos01'.

Witch Trigger: 'hanawitch'.

Weight: Between 0.7 / 1.

Example input:(casual)
(little girl), (masterpiece), highest quality, ((high detail:1.2)), (HDR), cel anime, (cinematic light:1.1), highres, (makihatayama_hana), 1girl, (full body), blonde hair, long hair, twintails, hair intakes, brown eyes, dot nose, (hanacos01), (blue shorts), (white shirt), (orange shoes), blue sky, park, <lora:hana_makihatayama_v3:0.8>

Example input:(witch)
1girl, solo, full body, cel anime, <lora:hana_makihatayama_v3:0.8>, (makihatayama_hana), blonde hair, long hair, hair intakes, brown eyes, dot nose, (hanawitch:2), white gloves, compact ,white dress, (yellow frills), puffy short sleeves ,white skirt, white boots, magical girl, hat, smile,
